@startuml
title Update Process (Level 1) — VendNet

actor "Actor\n(Operator/Admin)" as User
participant "VendNet System" as System

User -> System: Request Update with Data
activate System
System -> System: Validate & Process Update
alt Update Successful
    System --> User: Display Success Message
else Update Failed / Not Found
    System --> User: Display Error Message
end
deactivate System
@enduml